data.description: Beautiful Custom 4bd 3.5 bath Home Built in 2009 sits on 11.49 Total Acres including 2 Parcels. 2 Large Master Suites with their own Master Baths, along with beautiful views from all rooms. Nestled in the Mountains close to the entrance to the Sequoia National Park, Ton of Outdoor Activities in the Area including, fishing, hiking, biking, camping. This could also be a great Vacation Home or possible Airbnb. Ton of Possibilities.
